ign:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"margin:0;">In some ways, =
it seems, Senate Democrats have already lost the messaging war. Republicans=
 have spent days
framing a potential shutdown as a =E2=80=9CSchumer shutdown,=E2=80=9D while=
 Schumer has avoided talking about it. Certainly, the issue is hard; the up=
coming funding vote could be the most torturous that any Senate Democrat ha=
