ttom:0px;">Schumer=E2=80=99s defenders say the leader can=E2=80=99t be heav=
y-handed, and must consider the demands and concerns of his members as he t=
ries to navigate his caucus through an unprecedented situation with a mercu=
rial president. He=E2=80=99s cautious about careening toward a shutdown whe=
n
